{"tid":1728741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預計明日的繁忙時段由早上6時開始","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:13:02.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71e81fa19bdc2e8e582eeaa66268e20fc264a854","tid":1728741,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:59:12.000Z","msg":"班港豬咁鍾意返工，各位，are you ready?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdd8043ba2ab44eccfcdebf583a09a57426f379","tid":1728741,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"3b4f490218aa68567d0e1d3551aa6c09cc2eb4d0","tid":1728741,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］ 係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}